{"id":232915645,"title":"Chateau La voice, 泰國禮盒搭配的紅酒 (不專業分享）","content":"這瓶酒是泰國客人送的禮盒內的紅酒，酒標看起來很漂亮，想說應該是不錯的酒（價位不錯），結果網路一查均價279台幣，哇！比我整天喝的Yellow Tail還便宜，慘了，這一定跟經濟艙搭配的紅酒等級差不多。\n\nBut, 就是這個but, 在開瓶後一聞，嗯，莓果香氣不錯阿，沒有什麼過多其他味道，那就姑且一試味道看看。 一喝，順啦，又是一瓶喝起來很順暢的紅酒，跟上次喝Montes Alpha一樣，物美價廉，但這瓶酒感覺是Cabernet+Merlot調合的，跟上次喝的Syrah是不一樣的。 我不專業啦？酒標上沒寫就以感覺來猜看看吧。  \n\n台灣如果買的到，我一定卯起來囤。畢竟279一瓶好喝的酒去哪找啊。\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f75eac12-5053-412c-8e39-b80dc3ddef1c/1280.jpeg","excerpt":"這瓶酒是泰國客人送的禮盒內的紅酒，酒標看起來很漂亮，想說應該是不錯的酒（價位不錯），結果網路一查均價279台幣，哇！比我整天喝的Yellow Tail還便宜，慘了，這一定跟經濟艙搭配的紅酒等級差不多。","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"23082c2f-c19d-456c-a805-1e6ac0a36c31","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-18T16:04:45.976Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-18T16:04:45.976Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":5,"tags":[],"topics":["紅酒","喝酒","品酒板","品酒版"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"品酒","forumAlias":"alcohol","school":"加州大學戴維斯分校","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":5}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f75eac12-5053-412c-8e39-b80dc3ddef1c/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"9f768a42-782c-4361-a777-000b8a447db9","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f75eac12-5053-412c-8e39-b80dc3ddef1c/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f75eac12-5053-412c-8e39-b80dc3ddef1c/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f75eac12-5053-412c-8e39-b80dc3ddef1c/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-18T16:04:45.976Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-18T16:04:45.976Z","width":480,"height":640},{"id":"9f768a42-782c-4361-a777-000b8a447db9","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/image